title: VH1 I Love New York 2 Finale.avi
description:
Rasta Finale

After a season of ups and downs and a tense elimination in Miami, it&#039;s down to New York&#039;s final two suitors. They accompany New York to the tropics of Jamaica for the final showdown. Cliff-diving, horse-back riding, heated, passionate dinners and men literally climbing the walls of their room make up the heart of this can&#039;t miss episode. Who will New York choose to be her man? Sister Patterson makes a unexpected appearance to grill the two suitors, just to make sure her daughter picks the right one. But will New York finally listen?
